MODIFICATIONS
=============

The LIME team has made the following modifications to HuggingFace transformers code:

1. Added support for Layer-wise Relevance Propagation (LRP)
2. Implemented training-free inference-time K/V delta optimization
3. Added LIME descriptor and state management
4. Integrated modality enhancement mechanisms for multimodal models
5. Added relevance-based objective computation

All modifications are designed to:
- Maintain compatibility with the original Apache 2.0 license
- Preserve the ability to update from upstream HuggingFace
- Support research and reproducibility

